author.value: Finding aid prepared by Emilyn L. Brown (finding aid) and John Bence (inventory).

creation.value:
This finding aid was produced using the Archivists' Toolkit
                <date>2016-06-29T09:40-0400</date>

unittitle.value: Audiovisual Collection of the Research Institute for the Study of Man

abstract.label: Abstract
abstract.value: These tapes are not obviously part of any other RISM collections. They include 1/4" audio as well as cassette tapes. There are commercially produced music tapes in the collection as well.

p.value:
Published citations should take the following form:
